title: Vlastimil Karal
text:
Vlastimil Karal (born 26 April 1983) is a <a href="Czechs">Czech</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> defender currently playing for <a href="FK%20Bohemians%20Prague%20%28St%C5%99%C3%AD%C5%BEkov%29">Bohemians Prague</a> in the <a href="Czech%202.%20Liga">Czech 2. Liga</a>.
Career statistics.
"Statistics accurate as of 30 June 2013"
